&lt;/ol&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I built this project as a full-stack application to improve my skills in frontend, backend, real-time communication, and deployment. Along the way, I learned how to structure a project cleanly, handle authentication securely, and implement interactive features that feel smooth for users.&lt;/p&gt;

